{"tid":2245360,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"10月19日 道指急瀉22% 引發經濟衰退","createTime":"2020-10-16T07:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T02:09:29.000Z","uid":73241,"like":2,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"33bcf6d1a63dcd4d590387b53e295725aeee37b8","tid":2245360,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:21:37.000Z","msg":"香港時間早上10時，香港股市準時開市，惟恆生指數甫開市即受紐約影響恐慌性下瀉120點，中午收市下跌235點，全日收市共下跌420.81點，收市報3362.39（超過10%），各月份期指均下跌超過300點至跌停板。<br />\n<br />\n受香港暴跌影響，各亞太地區股市全面下瀉，效應並如骨牌般隨各時區陸續開市擴展至歐洲市場，並最終繞地球一圈回到紐約：道瓊工業平均指數在10月19日大幅下跌508點（逾20%）。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f399ef32fe326a83394eb3717d4edfd4170c2e95","tid":2245360,"uid":310914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:22:27.000Z","msg":"過幾日就夾死你班淡友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a4a10b72e150a7a538699990fdc64a72866032","tid":2245360,"uid":73241,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f399ef32fe326a83394eb3717d4edfd4170c2e95","tid":2245360,"uid":310914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:22:27.000Z","msg":"過幾日就夾死你班淡友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:24:17.000Z","msg":"1987年10月19日 黑色星期一<br />\n2020年10月19日 唔通係粉紅色星期一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1db023c6b20d9dcce4767cf66d5e51c0a3b691","tid":2245360,"uid":88878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:24:54.000Z","msg":"想用恐懼支配我<br />\n衰過共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a9c6a96c95a44c9df91f476ea27b3a4e36fb09","tid":2245360,"uid":32722,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score"